channel.title: [317] shroggscape v1 [317] UPDATED!
channel.description:
hey guys shrogg here.
i got bored one day and decided to make a server using devolution7.0
[size=20pt]please note, this is my first server and i am still learning[/size]
its still a work in progress but its all coming together nicely.
[size=15pt]coders[/size] main coder 1: me (shrogg) 2nd main coder: RID22
[size=15pt]admins[/size] shrogg tobias RID22
[size=20pt]updates[/size] added slayer med lvl training cave added tunnel to slayer fixed whip
heres some info
>this server has no bulk portals, (i see that in a lot of servers around) instead it has port sarim, you can catch the 3 boats to...
:entrancia (noob start point i call it) :draynoor (med lvl home basically) :burgh de rott (high lvl home)
>it doesn't have 1 home with multiple shops it has 3, but these "homes" don't have all of the shops, they are just a place for the people around that level to hang out.
>no bulk shops (why do people do it!)
>mini games aren't in one place, they are dotted around.
lol i am having a problem with the jad... hes only hitting 0's its kind of annoying
[size=20pt]working skills[/size] runecrafting strength attack defense herblore full smithing full mining hitpoints slayer

5) Projects: This is not the place to post minor projects, such as, changing spawn locations, adding a few commands then saying you will release. We don't want to see that you can change a number, we want to see that you can create something that will change the server in such a way that it'll make it funner and more enjoyable for the players, or that you can change the game code to make it more efficient at doing a certain task or to have more stability overall.
